==English==
===Alternative spellings===
*sometimes hyphenated or expressed as a phrase: '''pan-theistically''', '''pan theistically'''
*sometimes either the P or both the P and the initial T are capitalized: '''Pantheistically''', '''PanTheistically'''
*variations of capitalization and spacing may be combined: '''Pan-theistically''', '''Pan-Theistically''', '''Pan Theistically''', '''Pan theistically'''
===Etymology===
From {{Gr.}} ''[[πάν]]'' (pán) "all"
and ''[[θεός]] (Theós) "god".

